 q = \mathrm{Corr}(X_1,X_2)
\mathrm{Corr}(X_1,X_2)
 \mathrm{corr}(X_1,X_2) = {\mathrm{cov}(X_1,X_2) \over {\sigma_{X_1} \sigma_{X_2}}}
